INSTALLATION
==================

1. Extract the contents to a location of your choice
2. Drag the file "gg_SCNG_ice_world_v2.bsp" into you maps folder located: C:\program files(x86)\steam\steamapps\<yourname>\counter-strikesource\cstrike\maps


TO SEE THIS MAP IN ACTION:
66.55.131.14


-SCNG
